Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.84,0:01:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子 瞬間同化了很多意識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.82,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 百合作為首領做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.45,0:01:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避免了戰線最大的危機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.01,0:01:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 誰都沒有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方會在公會裡佈下大量的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.41,0:01:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以逸待勞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:01:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 那是奏的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷酷的奏想出的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她畢竟也是奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.72,0:02:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 謝謝你這樣說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說沒有醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒人會生病嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼還不醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnmingliu\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs120\pos(942,434)}在你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnmingliu\bord0\1c&H000000&\fs120\pos(1065,558)}記憶裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前所未聞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.27,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次碰到天使那種狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.98,0:02:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 她可能再也不會醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是特殊情況
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.75,0:02:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天她會醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果只是睡過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的她 會是哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椎名說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是非常重要的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此 這才是問題所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是哪個天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是最初的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.31,0:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們一起釣過魚的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但襲擊我們的意識全都好戰且冷酷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.02,0:03:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論數量可是以一敵百啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在她為什麼會失去意識？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半因為大量意識在她的小腦袋裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂成一團沒法收拾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.27,0:03:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要是醒來 會以過百的意識醒來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.62,0:03:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從比例看來 像先前那樣醒來的概率約為1%吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.88,0:03:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經採取了對策
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把竹山送入了天使領域
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和能夠翻譯手冊的朋友一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:03:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TK和松下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看TK那樣 英語完全不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除所有數據 變更登錄密碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印所有能力 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這樣只能應付一時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早晚會被突破 數據會被重新輸入
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就把電腦整個破壞掉好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.50,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦在電腦室裡有的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.34,0:04:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟件也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天大家腦子都很靈光嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.38,0:04:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非吃壞肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只能聽天命了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.64,0:04:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神到底會站在哪一邊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 考試時間已經過了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點頭暈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你額頭出血了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:05:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:05:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.23,0:06:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你是醫生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能 我只是個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.06,0:06:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之先求救
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去救裡面的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.94,0:06:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:47.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有點頭重腳輕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫五十嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.36,0:06:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.69,0:06:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.84,0:07:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能得救嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找出口
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.19,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能出去的話 我會去求援
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後一定會回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.80,0:07:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電筒借用一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.51,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要逃出生天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:07:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點困難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.81,0:09:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隧道前後都被落石封住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機也接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.98,0:09:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和外面聯繫不上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.27,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後要團結一心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.30,0:09:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想著獨自獲救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收集食物和水
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家平分
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候變成你指揮了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那誰來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.87,0:09:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來指揮照顧傷者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.38,0:09:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有醫學知識
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會拋下傷者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒不會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.31,0:09:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要忍過去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.31,0:09:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.90,0:10:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口渴了說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物會定時發放
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺不舒服就找音無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再堅持一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事請叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,食物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些自製便當和點心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飲品有五六瓶茶和水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最多撐三天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你還真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.79,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太奮不顧身了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.15,0:10:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去國外當義工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.55,0:10:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.01,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的 別當真
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.91,0:10:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也要保留一點體力哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.85,0:10:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心自己先倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.18,0:10:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙把水…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什… 什麼嘛 首領大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.18,0:11:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把我綁起來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨你的便 反正沒人能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 大家也都知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.26,0:11:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說漂亮話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才他把寶貴的水給…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.56,0:11:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是我的份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.79,0:11:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今後不會喝了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.84,0:11:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰去揍那傢伙一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然我沒法消氣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會好好教訓他的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.84,0:11:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 我們喝一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 把這傢伙帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無 音無
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.22,0:12:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況不妙 快來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.33,0:12:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在努力做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她… 初音教會了我生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 又眼睜睜地看著人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:23.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是如此無力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時一樣 沒有任何改變
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.00,0:13:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.41,0:13:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是先休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.74,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想再看一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 小心不要感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.61,0:13:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼好不了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有捐贈者就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捐贈者？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.39,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十嵐 你有簽字筆嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.71,0:15:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來 就算自己的生命結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這生命還能被他人使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.27,0:15:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就有了生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.20,0:15:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家本已如此絕望了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻卻都想把希望托付給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你拯救了大家的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.72,0:15:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.86,0:16:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 音無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音無
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 讓我擔心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 身體還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.11,0:16:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是場壯烈至極的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你約定過的我醒來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.85,0:16:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我全都想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死前的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前往考場的途中 遭遇了車禍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想做個醫生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.71,0:17:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為他人而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為那句謝謝而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一心這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命學習過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.17,0:17:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在最後的最後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過登記成捐贈者 把身體留了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.72,0:17:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的身體應該救了什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於素未謀面的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:47.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人肯定會一生感激的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結弦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你已經沒什麼留戀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.30,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拯救別人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.34,0:18:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.17,0:18:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 我會消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒有留戀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.88,0:18:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們還在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你想和他們永遠在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.24,0:18:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他們是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.51,0:18:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.12,0:18:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我現在有了新的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們也能像我這樣感覺得到了回報
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起從這個世上消失就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始一場新的人生也不壞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.64,0:18:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想把這份感受傳達給大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:18:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說一見面 我就被你捅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.27,0:19:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是你讓我證明你不會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兜了好大個圈子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙和他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而說到這傢伙的笨拙…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.30,0:19:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認真聽講幸福嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加社團活動會得到滿足嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.81,0:19:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為來這裡的人都沒能好好度過青春時代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.21,0:19:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.97,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.89,0:19:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你通過觀察沒有發覺到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.76,0:19:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是年輕的靈魂得到救贖的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向要是接住那個二壘高飛球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:19:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也會被救贖而消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和唯真是多此一舉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.70,0:19:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩澤通過自己的力量達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到救贖消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不是自願來到這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在和命運的不公抗爭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而奏說不盡如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.19,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想告訴他們何謂美滿的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.84,0:20:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想讓他們度過常人的青春歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.99,0:20:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而來說服在這裡止步不前的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼諷刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.12,0:20:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.50,0:20:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了貫徹彼此的信念而對立
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至造出了武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 每天都在爭鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:39.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底有多笨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.97,0:20:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你發現了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但是如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.00,0:20:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在的話 可能能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說 讓我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你應該已經消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你還留在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能成為你的第一個同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.50,0:21:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的留戀 不就是這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 直到那一天 我都相信自己是個好姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.11,0:21:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要守護的一切都在三十分鐘裡被奪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這種不近情理的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種人生 不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.45,0:21:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正因如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要永遠背負那份記憶的她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.17,0:21:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才必須被救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.35,0:21:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個笨拙的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.76,0:21:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不可能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.51,0:21:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那樣一來爭鬥會持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.35,0:21:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為他們的同伴 作為奏的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.24,0:21:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難道不該做點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.65,0:22:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你願幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要說的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.50,0:22:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在對天使說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.87,0:22:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該畢業了 從這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.99,0:22:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.29,0:22:25.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判明有人偷換了考試答題卡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.91,0:22:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企圖陷害立華
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立華自己證明了筆跡不一致
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.68,0:22:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而證明了立華的清白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.77,0:22:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復本校學生會長一職
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.86,0:22:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 圓滿完成會長代理一職的直井任副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 我為什麼要受這份罪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.53,0:22:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我們全都抓出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個旋轉飛行還有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.96,0:22:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.34,0:23:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 難得我們意見一致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份心情只有做過的人才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是旋轉飛行同志
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我脫衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.79,0:23:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫吧脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.14,0:23:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住口 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 好噁心 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她彷彿把這兩天的事情統統忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然 因為過百的一方獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,襲擊我們的那一方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.39,0:23:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那麼一瞬間 我還真以為她能成為同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.71,0:23:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要從他們口中問出過去的事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.62,0:23:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在失去了敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒法瞞著百合行動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.27,0:23:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以奏 希望你能繼續做學生會長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.61,0:23:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次和他們戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.25,0:23:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後按我的指示行動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.64,0:23:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 這一作戰很適合我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.02,0:23:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要讓你孤身一人了 抱歉
